title: Ep 172: Interview with Natalie Nahai - The Web Psychologist
description: Did you know that you can apply your psychology skills to the development of effective websites?  Meet one woman - Nathalie Nahai - who does exactly that and she has a background in not only psychology, but also Art, Physics and English Literature.  She's putting all those together to help people improve their websites and the power of their online influence, which by the way, is the title of the book she's working on: The Psychology of Online Influence.
